{"tid":632191,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意咗組仔，求屌醒","createTime":"2018-04-17T07:06:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T09:52:41.000Z","uid":2659,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"809daa601d0f6f830b8c48497b5474d6636bfa94","tid":632191,"uid":2659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"話說一直以黎同呢個組仔關係都唔錯，<br />\n住hall夜晚會一齊食飯飲酒傾計，但感覺只係好朋友<br />\n上個月我U有表演，我同佢講完咗想收禮物<br />\n表演前一日佢搵我問我想要咩，我話有心咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嗰時諗都應該只係因為係組仔先送比我姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知佢送咗個好得意嘅公仔比我，我個一刻個心即刻係「奶野」既感覺，feel到自己心動咗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然佢一直都冇提過自己有冇鍾意嘅人，但我知道佢一定唔會對我有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求屌醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6289661429fdb199efbf14bd147d3ecaa9c6a1","tid":632191,"uid":29126,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cabc10661749bd1711d9640582c0a42f5ea8dc26","tid":632191,"uid":147028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:08:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">去馬</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b1d2b2e5107f5a7d27b42a0d1f69c28cf93ed8","tid":632191,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:09:08.000Z","msg":"組你老味"},{"pid":"82582a9e116f9b725dec1fdff8a088f722bcb8b9","tid":632191,"uid":127272,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/17/150949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F17%2F150949_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0ef48e30&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8327179